VPC â†’ the whole network.

Subnet â†’ a smaller network inside VPC, e.g., public/private/database.

AZs â†’ copy subnets into multiple zones for reliability.

Terraform modules â†’ just calculate IP ranges and create the VPC/subnets automatically.

